msgid "Spawning monsters"
msgstr "產生怪物"

msgid ""
"In this part, we're going to spawn monsters along a path randomly. By the "
"end, you will have monsters roaming the game board."
msgstr ""
"在這一部分中，我們將沿著一條路徑隨機刷怪。在最後，怪物們就會在遊戲區域到處亂"
"跑了。"

